imal distributions on small family farms to do so he studies habitats within the farmland and how different animal populations interact with one another his work is largely informed by the need to crystallize the connection between diversity of life on the planet and the vital services that biodiversity provides to humanity tagged with discovery passion contact us follow us on twitter make a gift to h&s copyright 1997 2012 stanford university all rights reserved
